using campaign funds?

14:07.447 --> 14:10.183
I do not recall, Senator.

14:10.217 --> 14:12.586
Do you recall
any of the directives

14:12.619 --> 14:14.354
that you, uh, undertook

14:14.387 --> 14:16.923
at the Committee
to Re-elect the President?

14:16.957 --> 14:18.959
Uh, well, uh, that would
have to depend, of course,

14:18.992 --> 14:22.162
