you were referring to, Senator,

14:22.195 --> 14:25.131
but, uh, in general,
I would have to say that--

14:25.165 --> 14:27.033
That you do not recall?

14:27.067 --> 14:29.369
Uh, yeah, that's correct, Senator.

14:29.402 --> 14:33.206
Son, did you suffer
some acute brain injury

14:33.240 --> 14:35.475
