19:22.262 --> 19:24.797
You, um...

19:24.831 --> 19:25.899
you got some room in your bag

19:25.932 --> 19:27.567
for some of this here
mambo sauce?

19:31.604 --> 19:32.906
Mm-hmm.

19:38.845 --> 19:40.813
- Let's see what she learned.
- Yes, sir.

19:52.392 --> 19:54.661
Am I a winter or a spring?

19:54.694 --> 19:55.962
