19:56.195 --> 19:59.465
See, we have, uh,
olive undertones.

19:59.499 --> 20:01.401
- Is that bad?
- Mm.

20:01.434 --> 20:03.269
It's unique.

20:03.303 --> 20:05.204
Boys'll go nuts. Trust me.

