birthday was at a bar,

24:02.775 --> 24:06.045
I thought you meant something
more, you know, mellowed out.

24:06.078 --> 24:07.480
Stop.

24:07.513 --> 24:09.982
Everyone's gonna love you.
Don't overthink it.

24:10.016 --> 24:10.983
All right.

24:11.017 --> 24:12.685
<i>Janelle. Janelle!</i>

24:12.718 --> 24:15.154
Oh, hey.
