24:16.556 --> 24:19.458
- Hey!
- Hi!

24:19.492 --> 24:20.927
How's the birthday boy?

24:20.960 --> 24:23.763
Twenty-five and feeling fine,
thank you very much.

24:23.796 --> 24:26.232
Frank, this is Marc and Mary.

24:26.465 --> 24:27.733
They work
on the Watergate Committee.

24:27.767 --> 24:30.136
Guys, this is <i>the</i> Frank.

24:30.169 --> 24:32.905
Oh, Frank. Oh, my--
babe, this is Frank Wills.

24:32.939 --> 24:36.042
He is the security guard
who caught the guys.

24:36.075 --> 24:38.477
Holy shit, man.

24:38.511 --> 24:40.513
