in D.C. these days.

25:34.834 --> 25:36.903
Rest of us stuck
running on campus sit-ins.

25:36.936 --> 25:39.605
Well, hey, now, that is
heroic work too, so...

25:39.639 --> 25:40.873
Yeah, if you'd
show up more often.

25:40.907 --> 25:42.575
- Yeah.
- Whoo! Fair enough, sister.

25:42.608 --> 25:45.811
But this man, this man,

25:45.845 --> 25:47.213
