26:00.860 --> 26:02.862
A lot of people
would kill for that chance.

26:04.664 --> 26:07.300
Y-yeah, um...

26:07.333 --> 26:09.769
well, I--
there are a lot of, uh, issues

26:09.802 --> 26:12.605
I'd like to address
in the world currently,

26:12.638 --> 26:14.707
such as...

26:14.740 --> 26:16.609
mostly in some form
of helping other people,

26:16.642 --> 26:21.213
you know, to ensure them
that Frank Wills' name--

26:21.247 --> 26:23.149
I mean, that is my name--
um, to assure them

26:23.182 --> 26:26.919
that Frank Wills' name
is, um, mentioned

26:26.953 --> 26:30.323
not only in the Watergate
but, um, still in history.

26:30.356 --> 26:33.259
And I want to do some type
of form of, you know,

26:33.292 --> 26:35.695
helping humanitarians.

26:35.728 --> 26:36.829
I don't--I don't exactly have

26:36.862 --> 26:38.064
