of how to do that,

26:38.097 --> 26:41.267
but yeah, I wanna
do something to help somebody.

26:45.137 --> 26:47.807
Well, uh, I think it's time
for another round.

26:47.840 --> 26:50.009
- You a whiskey man?
- No.

26:50.042 --> 26:51.844
- You sure?
- I'm sure. Thank you.

26:51.877 --> 26:53.312
All right, brother.
I know you want something.

26:53.346 --> 26:55.181
Oh, okay.

26:55.214 --> 26:56.849
<i>Come on over here.</i>

26:56.882 --> 26:57.850
