through this week.

28:16.095 --> 28:17.096
Yeah.

28:19.765 --> 28:21.467
Couldn't do any of this
without you, you know?

28:23.302 --> 28:25.805
You make me better,
you really do.

28:25.838 --> 28:27.873
We make each other better,
