29:16.122 --> 29:17.356
Don't stay up too late.

29:17.389 --> 29:18.891
Okay.

29:39.812 --> 29:40.946
Fuck.

30:16.382 --> 30:18.184
<i>And now we resume
live coverage</i>

30:18.217 --> 30:20.152
<i>of the Senate Watergate hearings.</i>

30:20.186 --> 30:21.921
<i>Let's go talk to Dan Shore,</i>

30:21.954 --> 30:24.156
<i>who is outside
the committee room. Dan?</i>

30:24.190 --> 30:25.324
<i>Uh, yes, George.</i>

30:25.357 --> 30:26.425
<i>Uh, while you're looking
at John Dean,</i>

30:26.458 --> 30:28.894
I'm holding here
the first 98 pages

30:28.928 --> 30:31.830
of what's expected to be
140 pages of testimony

30:31.864 --> 30:33.532
that Mr. Dean
will be delivering today.

30:33.566 --> 30:35.334
<i>You ask me, John Dean's</i>

30:35.367 --> 30:37.269
<i>a half a gallon
of nothing much.</i>

30:37.303 --> 30:38.571
<i>What's he gonna give a nation</i>

30:38.604 --> 30:40.940
<i>so used
by this administration?</i>

30:40.973 --> 30:43.576
<i>But he do look slick,
I'll give him that.</i>

30:46.612 --> 30:47.947
<i>By his own admission,</i>

30:47.980 --> 30:49.481
<i>Mr. Dean was
a partial coconspirator</i>

30:49.515 --> 30:51.951
<i>in the president's alleged
