It's not about the apartment.

46:29.020 --> 46:30.188
Don't you get it?

46:32.190 --> 46:33.391
I don't belong here.

46:34.792 --> 46:36.995
This place...

46:37.028 --> 46:38.196
this place don't want me.

46:40.131 --> 46:43.268
Why would I fight to stay in
a place that doesn't want me?

46:43.301 --> 46:46.304
